                type="document" xml:id="d208">
                <head>208. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On November 17, the White House released a paper on the balance-of-payments
                    problem. In the field of international finance, it instructed the U.S.
                    Government to <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“(b) Continue urgently to insist that the other economically advanced
                            countries of the free world increase their share of the <hi
                                rend="italic">long-term,</hi> truly developmental type of financing
                            extended to the developing countries.” (Department of State <hi
                                rend="italic">Bulletin,</hi> December 5, 1960, page 862)</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>See <ref target="#d138">Document 138</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
